_sText:
This is DoomsDayArena, an idea which came to me. This is my first
serious css map im used to just making gmod maps.

This map has one way glass in two rooms either side of the main room so you can try and out-manuvoure your enemy. 

Nav file included, so if you wana play with bots you dont have to wait to create a nav.

This map was made for high numbers, 30-40 players, but lower numbers are still fun!

Thank you for downloading, Enjoy :D
